{"tid":444921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角擋大媽隔音屏或無入則 恐被政府取締","createTime":"2017-10-23T02:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T07:52:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"2caa0da1e188ade65a22b83f368b2df7779d230f","tid":444921,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171022/large/1508686670_57b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171022%2Flarge%2F1508686670_57b5.jpg&h=bcc5e8ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角行人專用區有店舖為阻擋街頭演唱的聲浪，在舖前加裝大型隔音屏障，香港測量師學會前會長何鉅業表示，此類屏障一般法例上並不容許興建，故相信店舖設屏障時未必有入則，他又認為若屏障興建時未有繫緊大廈結構，有機會因石屎鬆脫，令屏障跌下而對行人構成危險。<br />\n<br />\n何鉅業指出，以往不少店舖為遮擋太陽或擋風雨等，會在大廈加裝帆布伸縮簷篷，不同的是是次簷篷是接近垂直式設置而非一般橫向式，但相信結構相近，他指此類簷篷一般不會太重，故掉下來的風險不算高，但若簷篷未有繫緊大廈結構，「如果螺絲打得唔夠深，入不到大廈結構，或者舊樓結構較脆弱，石屎部份支撐唔夠，就可能有跌下來嘅風險」。<br />\n<br />\n何鉅業又認為，此類簷篷若阻擋整個店舖的門面，會阻礙通風，萬一發生意外，如火警等，或會影響消防員灌救火災，亦會阻礙救人及逃生，而簷篷平時亦會阻礙行人行過，對市民構成不便。至於此類建築是否需要入則，何鉅業表示，此類屏障在《建築物法例》上並不容許興建，故相信店舖未必有入則，或會被屋宇署等相關部門取締。<br />\n<br />\n記者 鍾雅宜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57365105&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57365105%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171023&d=VSLK3yOog%2BwHzqQje4Zk4MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=8408c49b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57365105%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171023&h=67358f05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57365105&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171023</a>"},{"pid":"15f476c18f54eb5178fee33666e3b0f556226e6d","tid":444921,"uid":82640,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"啲大媽應該被驅趕啦"},{"pid":"b8a26f1f4ca7cfa079a1e988a38e433cb647b170","tid":444921,"uid":114064,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"大媽：馬照跑，舞照跳"},{"pid":"799103324bb0fbd4e0cbe11d40b0df11f6a6d2e2","tid":444921,"uid":77092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb831f61c708357474917b26e27db7b36899056f","tid":444921,"uid":4917,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"大家都係中國人，佢唱歌你應該聽"},{"pid":"931e23c92727b0fecee7b975fa5329cc30779965","tid":444921,"uid":39200,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"一港兩制完美體現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7cc21dbc11b9d74703361dcb574aa7387850ac","tid":444921,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db6a9deb7623d05ab54a71a326d8d3b46aa2b2d5","tid":444921,"uid":93784,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"而家香港最矛盾既地方係<br />\n政府係唔屬於香港人<br />\n班大媽分分中有政治背景組織支持<br />\n警察,食環,環保署都奈佢地唔何<br />\n商戶唯有自己諗招對抗噪音整隔音屏<br />\n就比人用返法例話唔得要拆<br />\n但班大媽顛佬日日播到咁大聲跳老舞就無人解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57021021c2bf171ff6508945603b949fd78dfa7d","tid":444921,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依啲布地盤都有用<br />\n有撚用咩根本隔唔到音</blockquote><br />\n環保條例 地盤做左可能冇事 但唔做一定有事"},{"pid":"2cbddd7a4ac129683c91ebbd3afb387003c9d73d","tid":444921,"uid":13468,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"等待黃台仰重啓光復行動"},{"pid":"1328676aeddbae15a2cdb32c6c1de5f64f930486","tid":444921,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"學大陸人淘寶音波炮囉"},{"pid":"2f5d4bbae402c9